          <title>Kneepkens scores 32 as Utes hold off BYU, 81-76</title>
          <description><![CDATA[PROVO, Utah (ABC4 Sports) - The last time Gianna Kneepkens played against BYU, she suffered a season-ending knee injury in December of 2023. This time around, Kneepkens had one of the best days of her career.]]></description>
